#* c '''1667''', {{w|John Milton}}, ''[[s:Paradise Lost (1667)]]'', [[s:Paradise Lost (1667)#Book I|Book I]].
#*: Thus Satan...his other parts besides Prone on the flood, extended long and large, Lay floating many a '''rood'''...

